{
  "info": {
    "name": "JUKI API - Final Version",
    "description": "Koleksi API JUKI yang sudah disempurnakan.\n\n**Urutan Penggunaan:**\n1. **Auth > Register**: Membuat akun baru\n2. **Auth > Login**: Mendapatkan token\n3. **Profiles > Get My Profile**: Melihat status `trainingFlow` Anda\n4. **Payments > Upload**: Mengunggah bukti bayar\n5. **Admin > Flow Control > Verify Payment**: Admin memverifikasi pembayaran Anda\n6. ... dan seterusnya mengikuti alur pelatihan",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12345678"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "targetUserId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "currentEmail",
      "value": "user_123@juki.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "currentPassword",
      "value": "User123!",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health"]
            },
            "description": "Mengecek status kesehatan API"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const timestamp = new Date().getTime();",
                  "const email = `user_${timestamp}@juki.com`;",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set(\"currentEmail\", email);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{currentEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{currentPassword}}\",\n  \"fullName\": \"Test User {{currentEmail}}\",\n  \"nim\": \"{{$randomInt}}\",\n  \"phone\": \"0812{{$randomInt}}\",\n  \"birthPlace\": \"Jakarta\",\n  \"birthDate\": \"2000-01-01T00:00:00Z\",\n  \"gender\": \"MALE\",\n  \"faculty\": \"Teknik\",\n  \"major\": \"Informatika\",\n  \"studyProgram\": \"S1 TI\",\n  \"enrollmentYear\": 2023\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Membuat akun user baru dengan email yang di-generate otomatis"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.accessToken) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"accessToken\", jsonData.accessToken);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refreshToken\", jsonData.refreshToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{currentEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{currentPassword}}\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Login dan mendapatkan access token serta refresh token"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', pm.response.json().accessToken);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{refreshToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Memperbarui access token menggunakan refresh token"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Change Password",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"oldPassword\": \"{{currentPassword}}\",\n  \"newPassword\": \"NewSecret123!\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/change-password",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "change-password"]
            },
            "description": "Mengganti password akun"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "Logout dan menghapus session"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Profiles",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get My Profile",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (jsonData.userId) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"userId\", jsonData.userId);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/profiles/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["profiles", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan profil user yang sedang login. Gunakan ini untuk melihat status trainingFlow Anda (statusCode)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Profile",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"fullName\": \"Juki User Updated\",\n  \"phone\": \"081299998888\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/profiles/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["profiles", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Memperbarui informasi profil user"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Payments",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Payment Proof",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "description": "Gunakan file .jpg atau .png"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/payments/upload",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["payments", "upload"]
            },
            "description": "Mengunggah bukti pembayaran pelatihan"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Articles",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Upload Article",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "description": "Gunakan file .pdf"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/articles/upload",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["articles", "upload"]
            },
            "description": "Mengunggah artikel untuk review"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sessions",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Active Sessions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/sessions/me",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["sessions", "me"]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan daftar session aktif user"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "User Management",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "List Users",
              "event": [
                {
                  "listen": "test",
                  "script": {
                    "exec": [
                      "const jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                      "if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.length > 0) {",
                      "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"targetUserId\", jsonData.data[0].id);",
                      "}"
                    ],
                    "type": "text/javascript"
                  }
                }
              ],
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10&status=ACTIVE",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["users"],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "page",
                      "value": "1"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "limit",
                      "value": "10"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "status",
                      "value": "ACTIVE"
                    },
                    {
                      "key": "search",
                      "value": "",
                      "disabled": true
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Mendapatkan daftar semua user dengan pagination dan filter"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Get User Details",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{targetUserId}}",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["users", "{{targetUserId}}"]
                },
                "description": "Mendapatkan detail user berdasarkan ID"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Update User Status/Role",
              "request": {
                "method": "PATCH",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"status\": \"ACTIVE\",\n  \"role\": \"ADMIN\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/users/{{targetUserId}}",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["users", "{{targetUserId}}"]
                },
                "description": "Memperbarui status atau role user"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Flow Control",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "Verify Payment",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/payments/{{targetUserId}}/verify",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "payments", "{{targetUserId}}", "verify"]
                },
                "description": "Admin memverifikasi pembayaran user"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Complete Administrative",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/administrative/{{targetUserId}}/complete",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "administrative", "{{targetUserId}}", "complete"]
                },
                "description": "Menyelesaikan proses administratif user"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Setup OJS Account",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"ojs_user_test\",\n  \"password\": \"pass123\",\n  \"journalCode\": \"JUKI-VOL1\",\n  \"journalLink\": \"https://journal.juki.com\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/administrative/{{targetUserId}}/ojs",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "administrative", "{{targetUserId}}", "ojs"]
                },
                "description": "Membuat akun OJS untuk user"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Verify Article (OJS Check)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"comment\": \"Article confirmed in OJS system.\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/articles/{{targetUserId}}/verify",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "articles", "{{targetUserId}}", "verify"]
                },
                "description": "Memverifikasi artikel yang telah diupload di sistem OJS"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Accept Review & Finalize",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [
                  {
                    "key": "Content-Type",
                    "value": "application/json"
                  }
                ],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"comment\": \"Final review passed.\"\n}",
                  "options": {
                    "raw": {
                      "language": "json"
                    }
                  }
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/review-loa/{{targetUserId}}/review/accept",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "review-loa", "{{targetUserId}}", "review", "accept"]
                },
                "description": "Menerima hasil review final dan memfinalisasi proses"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Upload LOA (Final Step)",
              "request": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "formdata",
                  "formdata": [
                    {
                      "key": "file",
                      "type": "file",
                      "description": "PDF LOA (Letter of Acceptance)"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/admin/review-loa/{{targetUserId}}/loa/upload",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["admin", "review-loa", "{{targetUserId}}", "loa", "upload"]
                },
                "description": "Mengunggah Letter of Acceptance (LOA) sebagai langkah terakhir"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Audit Logs",
          "item": [
            {
              "name": "System Audit Logs",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/audit-logs?limit=50",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["audit-logs"],
                  "query": [
                    {
                      "key": "limit",
                      "value": "50"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "description": "Mendapatkan daftar audit logs sistem"
              },
              "response": []
            },
            {
              "name": "Audit Stats",
              "request": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": {
                  "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/audit-logs/stats",
                  "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
                  "path": ["audit-logs", "stats"]
                },
                "description": "Mendapatkan statistik audit logs"
              },
              "response": []
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{accessToken}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  }
}